<br>
About an hour before servers would go down for maintenance, the skys would all turn red and every area of the game became PvP.  The catch.....when servers came back up, everything would be restored to pre-frenzy state.<br>
<br>
So basically everyone went wild and different guilds took over different towns killing any non-guild that entered.  Rival guilds would &quot;invade&quot; the towns each other took over and fight for braggign rights.<br>
<br>
Friends would turn on friends and kill each other repeatedly.<br>
<br>
And then the servers would go down and come back up a few hours later and none of it ever happend....all was restored.<br>
